Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Boreal Forest
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Urban Masked
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.
Rare Special Items.lore: True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Scorched
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: The Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Safari Mesh
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.
Rare Special Items.lore: A predator is a predator, no matter the environment

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bowie Knife | Night
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: It's the whisper of the wind... it's the bite at your neck

Covert Skins.name: M4A4 | The Battlestar
Covert Skins.desc: All corners have been cut off the receipt of purchase.
Covert Skins.lore: Beware those who speak of the watchtower

Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Fuel Injector
Covert Skins.desc: The body of the rifle has been painted bright yellow and the magazine has been custom painted to look like machinery.
Covert Skins.lore: Live your life a quarter mag at a time

Classified Skins.name: AWP | Elite Build
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using a combination of hydrographics and careful stenciling and detailed with heat-transfer decals.
Classified Skins.lore: Chase Turner was a great man... you have big shoes to fill – The Phoenix and The Initiate, Part 1

Classified Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Kumicho Dragon
Classified Skins.desc: Dragons have been laser-etched onto the slide and grip.
Classified Skins.lore: I'm a big fan of your work Yukako, we should talk... -Huxley, The Competition

Classified Skins.name: Nova | Hyper Beast
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a beastly creature in psychedelic colors.
Classified Skins.lore: They call you The Oni, right? Such a scary name for such a sad man... – Elliot Kingsman, Mercenary

Restricted Skins.name: MAG-7 | Praetorian
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been distinguishly painted with metallics.

Restricted Skins.name: MP7 | Impire
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of a mob of imps,
Restricted Skins.lore: Decimation has never been so adorable

Restricted Skins.name: Glock-18 | Royal Legion
Restricted Skins.lore: Naomi understands that one day she will die for Valeria

Restricted Skins.name: FAMAS | Valence
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in a modern red and grey design that complements the weapon's form.

Restricted Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Triumvirate
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given a light blue DDPAT hydrographic as well as a custom painted slide.
Restricted Skins.lore: I don't profit from war, I profit from the human condition... - Booth, Arms Dealer

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Tec-9 | Jambiya
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted and laser-etched with middle eastern patterns.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Shahrazad told 1000 tales... this is the last one you'll hear

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAC-10 | Lapis Gator
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of vibrant alligator skin.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: USP-S | Lead Conduit
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a custom engraved silencer and slide.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: You got what you wanted, now do you know what that means? – Booth, Arms Dealer

Mil-Spec Skins.name: PP-Bizon | Photic Zone
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a custom camouflage pattern accented with florescent paint.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: That's not crashing waves you hear...

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SSG 08 | Necropos
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with nefarious runes.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Every carpenter needs their hammer, every tailor their spindle...

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Cartel
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been engraved with skeletons, flowers and serpents.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: That's why Huxley is doing the heavy lifting, all we have to is nudge her forward... - The Serpent and The Truth Seeker, Part 2
